INSERT INTO anime(title,synosis,image,studio,source,theme,score,opening) VALUES('My Home Hero','Tetsuo Tosu, an ordinary salaryman, discovers his daughter, Reika, has been physically abused by her boyfriend, Matori Nobuto. Trying to learn more about him, Tetsuo uncovers Matori''s scheme to extort money from Reika''s wealthy grandparents, and finds out that he is a member of a crime syndicate, with a history of murdering his former girlfriends.
INSERT INTO anime(title,synosis,image,studio,source,theme,score,opening) VALUES('Isekai Shoukan wa Nidome desu','There was once a man who was summoned to another world, and saved it. Of course, he became too popular there, and turned into an isekai-normie. However, that man fell into a "trap" and was forcibly returned to his original world. Moreover, he had to start over as a baby!
INSERT INTO anime(title,synosis,image,studio,source,theme,score,opening) VALUES('Skip to Loafer','Excellent student Iwakura Mitsumi has always dreamt about leaving her small town, going to a prestigious university, and making positive change in the world. But she''s so focused on reaching her goals that she''s not prepared for the very different (and overwhelming) city life that awaits her in a Tokyo high school. Luckily, she makes fast friends with Shima Sousuke, a handsome classmate who''s as laid-back as she is over-prepared. Can this naive country girl make it big in Tokyo with Sousuke by her side?
INSERT INTO anime(title,synosis,image,studio,source,theme,score,opening) VALUES('Otonari ni Ginga','Ever since their father died, Ichirou Kuga has struggled to support his two younger siblings on nothing but a small inheritance and his passion for drawing manga. But it''s becoming harder to keep up with his growing responsibilities and deadlines, especially after his last two assistants quit to follow their dreams. Just as he''s nearing his breaking point, the beautiful and scarily competent Shiori Goshiki applies to become his new assistant. But there''s something almost otherworldly about Goshiki, and soon Kuga finds his reality turned upside down when she suddenly declares them engaged to marry!
INSERT INTO anime(title,synosis,image,studio,source,theme,score,opening) VALUES('Tensei Kizoku no Isekai Boukenroku: Jichou wo Shiranai Kamigami no Shito','Teenager Shiinya Kazuya died while saving young girls from an attacker, only to find himself reincarnated into a world of swords and magic. It was a dream come true! Though he remembers his life and knowledge of Earth, he is now Cain von Silford, the third son of an aristocrat. Being granted the protection of the gods on his fifth birthday turned out to be too much of a good thing for Cain. His stats and boosts are so powerful, he must hide his real abilities to climb the ranks of society as he descends into the darkest dungeons. The ultimate isekai adventure begins as a teen-turned-child is trapped in a beautiful kingdom he didn''t create, but might one day rule!
INSERT INTO anime(title,synosis,image,studio,source,theme,score,opening) VALUES('Dead Mount Death Play','It''s a showdown for the ages as the legendary hero takes on the corpse god necromancer, but when the dust settles, something isn''t quite right... In the final moments of their epic confrontation, the corpse god''s final gambit shot was wholly unexpected—reincarnation magic! Across space and time, a boy named Polka Shinoyama awakens feeling...not quite himself... Who could''ve expected that the climactic battle between good and evil would turn out like this?
INSERT INTO anime(title,synosis,image,studio,source,theme,score,opening) VALUES('Kaminaki Sekai no Kamisama Katsudou','Yukito''s parents are the leaders of a cult. After he gets sacrificed, he gets reincarnated into another world where religion doesn''t exist and porn books are akin to a child''s doodles. He finds that it''s also a world where your life and death is decided by the country. While obstructing his friend''s execution, both of them lose their lives. Just at that moment, the god of his religion comes to their world and revives them.
