INSERT INTO anime(title,synosis,image,studio,source,theme,score,opening) VALUES('Yuusha ga Shinda!','Far to the north of the world lies Hell''s Gate, a portal formerly used by the Demon Lord to invade the human realm. Thanks to the legendary hero Shion Bladearts, wielder of Excalibur, and his loyal band of companions, the Gate was sealed off and the demonic threat was vanquished.
INSERT INTO anime(title,synosis,image,studio,source,theme,score,opening) VALUES('Kanojo ga Koushaku-tei ni Itta Riyuu','When Park Eunha dies in modern-day Korea, she awakens in the body of Raeliana McMillan, the eldest daughter of a nouveaux riche baron. However, this is no ordinary world; it''s the exact same one as a novel she once read. Beloved by her family, it would seem as though she is in a fairy tale. But Raeliana is far from the main character—she is a mere plot device, whose murder at the hands of her fiancé instigates the entire story.
